  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "United States, you need it from accredited school documents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "But a lot of other girls who did get nursing school in Hofgastein went in 1948 to Israel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And during the Israeli Independence War, they were very helpful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And they entire life worked in Israel because I was in touch with quite a few of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hofgastein was near Bad Gastein.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hofgastein was, was nearby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was maybe 10 kilometers away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The hospital was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bad Gastein was more of a resort-type of place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were there in 1946, when Leo, through the Briha-- one of our friends who brought us through Czechoslovakia, and, and through Vienna, he brought us to Salzburg and to Bad Gastein.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was the guide of the Briha.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was very friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We became very friendly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So when the trains where established, and whenever the big transfers from Poland came, and they came to Salzburg-- Salzburg was a transit place, and the Briha took them there.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From there, some of them went through Italy, to Italy, some to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some went to Germany to look for some friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Leo frequently was going to Salzburg, and he was looking always if somebody registered from our town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It so happened that it was not difficult, because some girls already was with somebody, somebody else, and they got married, so they wrote their married name.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if they mentioned that I was born in Lesko-- from there, Leo went a few times with the Briha group to Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got in touch-- he found my cousin, Rachel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My cousin Rachel was working in a little children's nursery there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Or in a children's-- in a little-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, in-- with children-aged kids.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was working there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
